      <h2>About This Project</h2>
      <p>
        This site tracks meteorite fireballs, AMS reports, and known meteorite finds,
        focusing on Arizona, Northern Sonora, and the Western USA.
        <br />
        Data sources: <a href="https://cneos.jpl.nasa.gov/fireballs/" target="_blank">NASA CNEOS</a>,
        <a href="https://www.amsmeteors.org/" target="_blank">AMS</a>,
        and the <a href="https://www.lpi.usra.edu/meteor/" target="_blank">Meteoritical Bulletin Database</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
